          Professional Care with a <span class="text-primary"
            >Personal Touch</span
          >
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg opacity-80 leading-relaxed">
          At Touching Hearts, we believe premium healthcare should be accessible
          and comfortable. Our board-certified team brings hospital-grade IV
          therapy and home health services directly to your living room.
        </p>
        <p class="opacity-80 leading-relaxed">
          Founded on the principles of integrity, safety, and clinical
          excellence, we specialize in preventative wellness and recovery. Every
          treatment is administered under strict medical protocols to ensure
          your safety and optimal results.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
              >check_circle</span
